Arcane Dabbler					KEY:Trait ~ Arcane Dabbler					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.RaceTrait.ElfTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Arcane Dabbler],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]			PRERACE:1,Elf%,RACESUBTYPE=Elf				DESC:Though your magical studies were decades ago, you still remember your favorite little trick. Choose a 0-level arcane spell. You may cast that spell once per day as a spell-like ability. Your caster level is equal to your highest class level in a spellcasting class; if you have no caster level, it functions at CL 1st. The spell-like ability's save DC is Intelligence- or Charisma-based (chosen when you select this trait).		SOURCEPAGE:p.15
Lapsed Faith					KEY:Trait ~ Lapsed Faith					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.RaceTrait.ElfTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Lapsed Faith],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]			PRERACE:1,Elf%,RACESUBTYPE=Elf				DESC:You still remember a few prayers from your past experience serving in a temple. Once per day you may cast cure minor wounds as a spell-like ability at caster level 1. The save DC is Wisdom-based.																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.15	SPELLS:Lapsed Faith|TIMES=1|TIMEUNIT=DAY|CASTERLEVEL=1|Cure Light Wounds
Seeker of Brightness				KEY:Trait ~ Seeker of Brightness				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.RaceTrait.ElfTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Seeker of Brightness],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]		PRERACE:1,Elf%,RACESUBTYPE=Elf				DESC:You have been actively searching for signs of the Brightness since childhood. Choose a Knowledge skill; you gain a +1 trait bonus on Knowledge checks of that type and on Search checks.																																										SOURCEPAGE:p.15	BONUS:SKILL|%LIST,Perception|1|TYPE=Trait	CHOOSE:SKILL|TYPE=Knowledge	MULT:YES	STACK:NO
Warrior of Old					KEY:Trait ~ Warrior of Old					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.RaceTrait.ElfTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Warrior of Old],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]			PRERACE:1,Elf%,RACESUBTYPE=Elf				DESC:As a child, you put in long hours in combat drills, and though time has made this training a dim memory, you still have a knack for quickly responding to trouble. You gain a +2 trait bonus on Initiative checks.																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.15	BONUS:COMBAT|INITIATIVE|2|TYPE=Trait
Youthful Mischief					KEY:Trait ~ Youthful Mischief					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.RaceTrait.ElfTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Youthful Mischief],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]			PRERACE:1,Elf%,RACESUBTYPE=Elf				DESC:Though you gave up the life of a padfoot, scout, or minstrel decades before, you still know how to roll with the punches when things turn sour. You gain a +1 trait bonus on Reflex saves.																																										SOURCEPAGE:p.15	BONUS:SAVE|Reflex|1|TYPE=Trait

