# Ability Name					Unique Key					Product Identity?	Category of Ability		Type							Multiple Requirements																											Required Race				Desc is PI?		Description																																																																								Source Page
Forlorn (Any non-elven land)			KEY:Trait ~ Forlorn						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.RegionalTrait		PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Forlorn],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RegionalTrait]													DESC:Having lived outside of traditional elf society for much or all of your life, you know the world can be cruel, dangerous, and unforgiving of the weak. You gain a +1 trait bonus on Fortitude saving throws.																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.15	BONUS:SAVE|Fortitude|1|TYPE=Trait
Iadaran Illusionist (Kyonin)			KEY:Trait ~ Iadaran Illusionist	NAMEISPI:YES	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.RegionalTrait		PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Iadaran Illusionist],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RegionalTrait]								DESCISPI:YES	DESC:You have lived in Iadara for so long that you are very familiar with illusions. You gain a +1 trait bonus on caster level checks with illusion spells and a +1 trait bonus on Will saves to disbelieve illusions.																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.15	BONUS:CASTERLEVEL|SCHOOL.Illusion|1|TYPE=Trait	ASPECT:SaveBonus|+1 trait bonus on Will saves to disbelieve illusions.	
Kyonin Gatekeeper (Kyonin)			KEY:Trait ~ Kyonin Gatekeeper		NAMEISPI:YES	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.RegionalTrait		PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Kyonin Gatekeeper],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RegionalTrait]											DESC:You helped maintain the elf gates and are familiar with the operation of teleportation magic. You gain a +1 trait bonus on Spellcraft checks to identify teleportation magic and a +1 trait bonus to caster level checks when casting teleportation spells. You know the proper commands to operate a particular elf gate (most likely an often used elf gate, but at the GM's discretion it may be a less popular or out-of-the-way elf gate).	SOURCEPAGE:p.15	ASPECT:SkillBonus|+1 trait bonus on Spellcraft checks to identify teleportation magic	BONUS:CASTERLEVEL|SUBSCHOOL.Teleportation|1|TYPE=Trait
Left Behind (Mwangi Expanse or Varisia)	KEY:Trait ~ Left Behind			NAMEISPI:YES	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.RegionalTrait		PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Left Behind],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RegionalTrait]									DESCISPI:YES	DESC:Having been born to those who chose to remain on Golarion during the Age of Darkness in the Mwangi Expanse, you understand the people of this world better than most elves. You gain a +1 trait bonus on Diplomacy and Gather Information checks when interacting with Forlorn elves and non-elf races.																							SOURCEPAGE:p.15	ASPECT:SkillBonus|+1 trait bonus on Diplomacy and Gather Information checks when interacting with Forlorn elves and non-elf races
Mordant Heritage (Mordant Spire)		KEY:Trait ~ Mordant Heritage		NAMEISPI:YES	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.RegionalTrait		PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Mordant Heritage],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RegionalTrait]								DESCISPI:YES	DESC:You lived among the Mordant Spire elves and know their strange ways. You gain a +1 trait bonus on Swim checks and a +1 trait bonus on saving throws against enchantment effects.																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.15	BONUS:SKILL|Swim|1|TYPE=Trait	ASPECT:SaveBonus|+1 trait bonus on saving throws against enchantment effect
Treerazer's Bane (Kyonin)			KEY:Trait ~ Treerazer's Bane		NAMEISPI:YES	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.RegionalTrait		PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Treerazer's Bane],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RegionalTrait]								DESCISPI:YES	DESC:Having fought in many battles against Treerazer and his minions, you have learned the best ways to kill the various creatures under his control. You gain a +2 trait bonus on weapon damage against demons, evil fey, and plants and animals corrupted by evil.																														SOURCEPAGE:p.15	ASPECT:CombatBonus|+2 trait bonus on weapon damage against demons, evil fey, and plants and animals corrupted by evil


